nodes.text: Kateena was a child who lived in an orphanage on the planet Jakku. Sometime before the Battle of Jakku, Kateena became wayward after being wooed by Gallius Rax and found a purpose away from the faith of anchorite Kolob. After fulfilling their purpose, Kateena along with other orphans such as Brev and Narawal were killed by Rax in order for him to keep a secret.
